The paper focuses on data exploration and processing, which is a core topic in database systems (cs.DB) and data structures (cs.DS). The use of online aggregation and sampling techniques also relates to information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses parallel processing and resource-aware algorithms, which are relevant to distributed computing (cs.DC).
